MySQL Server & Workbench Installation 

Check mysql version:
	mysql –version

Installation:
sudo apt-get install mysql-server
sudo nala install mysql-server

sudo mysql

create user 'username’@'localhost' identified by 'password';

grant all privileges on *.* to 'username’@'localhost';

cd ~
cd Downloads
ls
sudo nala install ./mysql-workbench-community_8.0.34-1ubuntu22.04_amd64.deb
 
    • Open workbench > Create a new connection >Using username & password > Delete Root connection

Delete mysql from Ubuntu:

  924  sudo apt-get remove --purge 'mysql*'
  925  sudo apt-get autoremove
  926  sudo apt-get autoclean

